fits for teams as they enhance the accuracy with\nwhich they make player acquisitions. The universal distribution we observed\nalso has many possible future applications throughout the sports world.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 18 Jun 2022 01:54:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-22"}
