 from the molecular cloud complexes in which\nclouds reside, and probably (iv) from massive young stellar complexes, if they\nwere present. (v) Finally, our results also suggest that, interstellar\nturbulence can have, at least partially, a gravitational origin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 18 Jun 2022 11:47:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-20"}
