ystals having three\nsymmetric planar tilt GBs. The compatibility of the microstructures across the\nGBs is studied. The elastic and structural stresses across the GBs and TJ\nregions are plotted, which is essential for understanding the role of GBs and\nTJs in materials failure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 18 Jun 2022 04:51:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-24"}
